entries.title_d: Remain in the Dathomir system and rescue a damaged Imperial Lambda shuttle. Once inside the system, you will receive a navigation waypoint to the shuttle's location. The shuttle is damaged and currently unable to move. You will need to travel to the shuttle's location and assist it with repairs. When you reach the shuttle, target it and use the /dock command to assist it with repairs. Once the shuttle is repaired, escort it through the system.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Rescue the Lambda Shuttle

entries.taunt_5: I almost feel sorry for what I am about to do to you.
entries.taunt_4: The galaxy doesn't need you kind around.
entries.taunt_3: Time to pay for your crimes, Imperial dog.
entries.taunt_2: The Alliance will never let you escape.
entries.taunt_1: You will not make it out of here alive!
entries.split_quest_alert: We believe that we located a command ship. During that fight we detected encrypted signals being sent to the fighters. We want whatever information that ship might have.
entries.rescue_phase_2: Ok, we are all hooked up. Let's try to get out of here.
entries.rescue_phase_1: I am really glad to see you. I don't know how much longer I could have held out.
entries.rescue_abandoned: What are you doing? We cannot hold out without your support.
entries.recovery_success: The shuttle is beginning jump procedure. Stand by until it is safely out of the system.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dathomir system and assist the damaged Imperial Lambda shuttle with repairs. You will receive a navigation waypoint of the damaged shuttle's location. Travel to that waypoint to meet up with the shuttle.
entries.quest_escort_d: Once the Imperial Lambda shuttle is repaired, follow it to its destination. Keep on guard! Because this shuttle is weakened prey, it will certainly draw the enemy's attention.
entries.quest_dock_d: When you arrive at the shuttle's location, target it, and use the /dock command in order to assist the shuttle with repairs.
entries.panic_5: Where are all these rebels coming from?
entries.panic_4: Why me? All I wanted was a nice quite flight.
entries.panic_3: My ship can't take many hits. You better be good.
entries.panic_2: Look out! There are more of them out there.
entries.panic_1: Where are all these Rebels coming from?
entries.failed_destroy: Pilot, the shuttle has been destroyed. Return to your superior and make a full report.
entries.docking_complete: Docking procedure completed. Stand by to escort shuttle out of danger area.
entries.complete: The shuttle is safe. Nice work, pilot.
entries.arrival_phase_2: We are sending the location of the shuttle to your nav computer. Proceed to that location immediately and rescue our ship.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Retreiving last known location of the shuttle. Stand by.
entries.abort: What are you doing? We cannot hold out without your support.
